OL,3,CWoman awarded #320,000 after bowel cut
OL,4,Cduring routine operation
OL,6,FA woman has been awarded #320,000 in
OL,7,Fdamages after doctors caused long-
OL,8,Flasting damage to her bowel during
OL,9,Fsurgery to remove her gallbladder.
OL,11,FCheryl Gravil, from Doncaster,
OL,12,Fsuffered the injury during what should
OL,13,Fhave been a routine operation at
OL,14,FDoncaster Royal Infirmary in 2017.
OL,16,FMedics initially failed to realise
OL,17,Fwhat had happened. It was only after
OL,18,Fshe complained of feeling unwell that
OL,19,Fthe problem was diagnosed.
