OL,6,FHaving initially been told she would
OL,7,Fspend less than a day in hospital, Ms
OL,8,FGravil instead spent four months
OL,9,Fbattling sepsis, pneumonia and a
OL,10,Fseries of other infections.
OL,12,F"I was later told that I'd have only
OL,13,Fsurvived another couple hours had I
OL,14,Fnot been admitted to intensive care
OL,15,Fwhen I was," she said.
OL,17,FFollowing her initial operation,
OL,18,Fnurses told Ms Gravil that it was
OL,19,Fcommon to feel unwell and she was
OL,20,Flikely experiencing wind.
