OL,6,F"When my husband arrived that
OL,7,Fafternoon he found me crying in pain
OL,8,Fand he insisted that I be seen by a
OL,9,Fdoctor," she said.
OL,11,F"I remember being told I may need an x-
OL,12,Fray and possibly surgery, and then the
OL,13,Fnext thing I can remember is waking up
OL,14,Fin intensive care with all these tubes
OL,15,Fcoming out of me and a colostomy bag."
OL,17,FShe later found out about the damage
OL,18,Fto her bowel and was told the
OL,19,Finfection was so extensive a large
OL,20,Farea would need removing.
