OL,6,F"My life has completely changed as it
OL,7,Fas left me with so many problems," she
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"As soon as I eat, the moment I put my
OL,11,Fknife and fork on the plate I feel
OL,12,Fawful. I have awful wind that I can't
OL,13,Fget rid of and i often have to be sick.
OL,15,F"It is awful to live with and it will
OL,16,Fbe lifelong now."
