OL,3,CWoman awarded #320,000 after bowel cut
OL,4,Cduring routine operation
OL,6,FDoncaster and Bassetlaw Teaching
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust
OL,8,Fadmitted negligence, saying that
OL,9,Frepair surgery would have been carried
OL,10,Fout immediately if the injury had been
OL,11,Fspotted sooner.
OL,13,FThe trust awarded #350,000 in an out-
OL,14,Fof-court settlement, covering damages
OL,15,Ffor her injuries and loss of earnings
OL,16,Fas she has been unable to return to
OL,17,Fwork.
