OL,3,CWoman awarded #320,000 after bowel cut
OL,4,Cduring routine operation
OL,6,FElizabeth Maliakal, of Hudgell
OL,7,FSolitcitors, which represented her,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Cheryl suffered several
OL,9,Finjuries due to failures in her
OL,10,Fmedical care and many setbacks on her
OL,11,Froad to recovery.
OL,13,F"She is now able to put this claim
OL,14,Fbehind her and use the damages awarded
OL,15,Fto access treatments she otherwise may
OL,16,Fnot have been able to afford or which
OL,17,Fmay not have been readily available on
OL,18,Fthe NHS."
